@startuml
!include _style.puml
title AS-IS 03 В· лҸ„л©”мқё нҒҙлһҳмҠӨмҷҖ м ҖмһҘ м ңм•Ҫ
left to right direction

class Payload {
  version : 2
  app : AppState
  atlas : AtlasState
  bridge : BridgeState
}

class AppState {
  version : 4
  progress : Map<ItemId, Progress>
  notes : Map<ItemId, String>
  settings : Object
}

class AtlasState {
  concepts : Concept[*]
  frames : Frame[*]
  objects : AtlasObject[*]
  keywords : String[*]
}

class BridgeState {
  links : StudyConceptLink[*]
  orphanedLinks : OrphanedLink[*]
  catalog : CatalogItem[*]
}

class Concept {
  id : String
  title : String
  conceptRole : core|support|general
  importance : Number
  primaryParent : ConceptId?
  parents : ConceptId[*]
  related : ConceptId[*]
  sections : SectionMap
  createdAt : DateTime?
  updatedAt : DateTime?
}

class ConceptLine {
  id : String
  text : String
  keywords : String[*]
}

class Frame {
  id : String
  type : String
  anchorId : ConceptId?
  members : EntityId[*]
  config : Object
}

class AtlasObject {
  id : String?
  payload : Object
}

class CatalogItem {
  id : String
  subject : String
  section : String
  name : String
}

class StudyConceptLink {
  itemId : ItemId
  conceptId : ConceptId
  role : String
}

class OrphanedLink {
  itemId : ItemId
  conceptId : MissingConceptId
  role : String
  reason : String
  archivedAt : DateTime?
}

class Workspace {
  syncId : String
  writeHash : String
  headRevision : Integer
}

class Revision {
  revision : Integer
  operationId : UUID
  payloadHash : String
  appState : JSON
  atlasState : JSON
  bridgeState : JSON
}

class SyncMeta {
  serverRevision : Integer
  lastPayloadHash : String
  dirty : Boolean
  generation : Integer
  restorePending : Boolean
}

Payload "1" *-- "1" AppState
Payload "1" *-- "1" AtlasState
Payload "1" *-- "1" BridgeState
AtlasState "1" *-- "0..*" Concept
Concept "1" *-- "0..*" ConceptLine
AtlasState "1" *-- "0..*" Frame
AtlasState "1" *-- "0..*" AtlasObject
BridgeState "1" *-- "0..*" StudyConceptLink
BridgeState "1" *-- "0..*" OrphanedLink
BridgeState "1" *-- "0..*" CatalogItem
StudyConceptLink "0..*" --> "1" CatalogItem : itemId [S]
StudyConceptLink "0..*" --> "1" Concept : conceptId [S][D]
Concept "0..*" --> "0..*" Concept : parent В· related
Frame "0..*" --> "0..1" Concept : anchorId
Frame "0..*" --> "0..*" Concept : member
Frame "0..*" --> "0..*" AtlasObject : member
Workspace "1" *-- "0..*" Revision
SyncMeta ..> Workspace

note right of ConceptLine
  [D] SQL PKлҠ” (sync_id, line_id).
  line IDлҠ” workspace м „мІҙм—җм„ң мң мқјн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.
end note

note right of StudyConceptLink
  кІ°н•Ё 11 [D]
  DB PK = (sync_id,item_id,concept_id).
  к°ҷмқҖ pairмқҳ лӢӨмӨ‘ roleмқҖ projectionм—җм„ң м¶•м•ҪлҗңлӢӨ.
end note

note bottom of Concept
  projection мҶҗмӢӨ [D]
  primaryParent, кҙҖкі„ л°°м—ҙ мҲңм„ң,
  мһ„мқҳ нҷ•мһҘ н•„л“ңлҠ” normalized tableм—җм„ң
  мҷ„м „нһҲ н‘ңнҳ„лҗҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
end note

note bottom of Frame
  [D] anchor FKлҠ” delete set null.
  memberмқҳ лӢӨнҳ• м°ёмЎ°лҠ” entity FK лҢҖмӢ 
  RPC assertм—җ мқҳмЎҙн•ңлӢӨ.
end note

note bottom of SyncMeta
  кІ°н•Ё 3 [S]
  META_KEY н•ҳлӮҳм—җ revision/hashк°Җ м ҖмһҘлҗҳм–ҙ
  workspace ліҖкІҪ л’Ө мқҙм „ к°’мқҙ лӮЁмқ„ мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ.
end note

caption revision JSONкіј normalized projectionмқҖ нҳ„мһ¬ лҸҷмқјн•ң н‘ңнҳ„л Ҙмқ„ к°–м§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.
@enduml
